        </div>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3">Skill-based search</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary">Find colleagues by specific skills - React, UX research, Python, or any expertise. See who knows what in seconds.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>
                    </div>
