                    <p class="text-secondary">Discover ongoing projects that need your skills. Join teams that align with your expertise and interests.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    </div>
